CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. A6, reads: "Birthday Fun - A gay birthday party was given for Mr. and Mrs. Winsted of 2801 Bedford Ave., by her daughter, Betty, who attends college in New New [sic] York City.  Many friends and neighbors attended the gay affair."
TitMainTitle: Margaret Bullard or Winsted feeding cake to Mr. Winsted, in kitchen for birthday party in their home, 2801 Bedford Avenue, Hill District
